#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/cdi-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus DI solution (also called ArC) is based on the https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html[Jakarta Contexts and Dependency Injection 4.1, window=\"_blank\"] specification.\n"
"It implements the CDI Lite specification, with selected improvements on top, and passes the CDI Lite TCK.\n"
"It does not implement CDI Full.\n"
"See also <<supported_features_and_limitations,the list of supported features and limitations>>.\n"
"Most of the existing CDI code should work just fine but there are some small differences which follow from the Quarkus architecture and goals."
msgstr "A soluĂ§ĂŁo Quarkus DI (tambĂ©m chamada de ArC) Ă© baseada na especificaĂ§ĂŁo link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html[Jakarta Contexts and Dependency Injection 4.1] . Ela implementa a especificaĂ§ĂŁo CDI Lite, com aprimoramentos selecionados no topo, e passa pelo TCK do CDI Lite. Ele nĂŁo implementa o CDI Full. Consulte tambĂ©m xref:supported_features_and_limitations[a lista de recursos e limitaĂ§Ăµes compatĂ­veis] . A maior parte do cĂłdigo CDI existente deve funcionar perfeitamente, mas hĂˇ algumas pequenas diferenĂ§as que decorrem da arquitetura e dos objetivos do Quarkus."

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/cdi-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you're new to CDI we recommend you to read the xref:cdi.adoc[Introduction to CDI] first."
msgstr "Se o senhor for novo no CDI, recomendamos que leia primeiro a xref:cdi.adoc[IntroduĂ§ĂŁo ao CDI] ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/cdi-reference.adoc
