#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/cdi-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `io.quarkus.runtime.BlockingOperationControl#isBlockingAllowed()` method can be used to detect whether blocking is allowed on the current thread.\n"
